import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Button, Box, Grid, Card, CardContent } from '@mui/material';
import LoginSignupBox from './LoginSignupBox';
import SetMealIcon from '@mui/icons-material/SetMeal';

function HomePage() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: '#102539', minHeight: '100vh', paddingTop: 4 }}>
      <Container maxWidth="sm" sx={{ mb: 5 }}>
        {/* Log In / Sign-Up Card */}
        <Card sx={{ backgroundColor: '#00522D', color: '#ffffff', padding: 4, borderRadius: 2 }}>
          <LoginSignupBox />
        </Card>
      </Container>

      {/* Hero Section */}
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ backgroundColor: '#102539', paddingY: 5, borderRadius: 2 }}>
        <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', marginBottom: 5 }}>
          <Typography variant="h3" gutterBottom color="primary.contrastText">
            Discover the Best Fishing Tournaments Online
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom color="primary.contrastText">
            Participate, compete, and win in our well-organized online fishing tournaments. Get started today!
          </Typography>
        </Box>

        {/* Information Cards */}
        <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center">
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ backgroundColor: '#C8A57F', color: '#000000', padding: 3, borderRadius: 2 }}>
              <CardContent>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', marginBottom: 2 }}>
                  <SetMealIcon fontSize="large" color="inherit" />
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                  Easy Sign Up
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2">
                  Create an account in just a few steps and start competing in online fishing tournaments.
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ backgroundColor: '#C8A57F', color: '#000000', padding: 3, borderRadius: 2 }}>
              <CardContent>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', marginBottom: 2 }}>
                  <SetMealIcon fontSize="large" color="inherit" />
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                  Find Tournaments
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2">
                  Browse through a variety of tournaments, filter by location, type, and target species.
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ backgroundColor: '#C8A57F', color: '#000000', padding: 3, borderRadius: 2 }}>
              <CardContent>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', marginBottom: 2 }}>
                  <SetMealIcon fontSize="large" color="inherit" />
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                  Submit Catches
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2">
                  Upload photos of your catches and see how you rank against other anglers in real-time.
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default HomePage;
